CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 12, 1961, pg. 20, reads: "Six Tan Aces in Jaycee All-Star Game - They'll Cheer Heroes - Left to right: Susan Norseen, Marsha Crouse, Laura Oberheim, Rosalind Federchak, Lynne Lippincott, Joanne Shingler, Linda Koslow.  Standing: Ann Katherine Woods, 'Miss Jaycee of 1960.'... - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: All-Star Jaycee football game cheerleaders, from left: Susan Norseen, Marsha Crouse, Laura Oberheim, Rosalind Federchak, Lynne Lippincott, Joanne Shingler, Linda Koslow, and "Miss Jaycee of 1960" Ann Katherine Woods in back, posed on field
